            <div class="border-l-4 border-teal-500 pl-4">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">1. UX & UI Standards for Cognitive Disability</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Core engineering requirements derived from WCAG 2.2 and W3C COGA to minimize cognitive load and prevent errors.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Focus & Load Section -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="p-6 border-b border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 flex justify-between items-center">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-800">Critical Success Criteria (WCAG 2.2 / COGA)</h3>
                    <span class="text-xs font-mono bg-slate-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">Dev Requirements</span>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
                    
                    <!-- Criteria 1 -->
                    <div class="p-4 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg bg-slate-50">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="text-2xl mt-1">üéØ</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-800">Focus & Persistence</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal-600 mb-2">WCAG 2.4.7, 2.4.11</p>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-3">Users with reduced working memory may lose their place. Interface elements must not disappear automatically.</p>
                                <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 list-disc list-inside bg-white p-3 rounded border border-slate-100">
                                    <li>Focus indicators must have <strong>3:1 contrast</strong>.</li>
                                    <li>Tooltips must be <strong>persistent</strong> (dismissible by Escape key only).</li>
                                    <li>No time-outs on reading content.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Criteria 2 -->
                    <div class="p-4 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg bg-slate-50">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="text-2xl mt-1">üõë</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-800">Error Prevention</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal-600 mb-2">WCAG 3.3.4, 3.3.8</p>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-3">Anxiety increases error rates. Reversible actions are critical.</p>
                                <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 list-disc list-inside bg-white p-3 rounded border border-slate-100">
                                    <li>Implement <strong>"Accessible Authentication"</strong> (no memory tests/puzzles).</li>
                                    <li>All form submissions require a <strong>Confirmation Step</strong>.</li>
                                    <li>Input fields must support <strong>autocomplete</strong> to reduce typing.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Design Pattern Demo -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-800 mb-4">Design Pattern: Linear Navigation</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-6">Users with attention deficits struggle with "Dashboard" layouts that have multiple competing calls to action. The UI must be strictly linear.</p>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <!-- Bad Example -->
                    <div class="border-2 border-red-100 rounded-xl p-4 opacity-75 decoration-element">
