                        </div>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2">Multiple columns, sidebars, and competing attention grabbers overwhelm the user.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Good Example -->
                    <div class="border-2 border-teal-100 rounded-xl p-4 bg-teal-50/30">
                        <div class="text-xs font-bold text-teal-600 uppercase mb-2">‚úÖ Linear Flow (Recommended)</div>
