                            <div class="w-3/4 h-4 bg-slate-200 rounded"></div>
                            <div class="w-1/2 h-8 bg-teal-500 rounded text-white text-xs flex items-center justify-center">One Action</div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2">Single column, one primary action per screen, distinct "Back" and "Next" buttons.</p>
                    </div>
