                                Implement a non-verbal "Panic Button" in the navbar that immediately simplifies the interface and offers help options.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Competitor 2 -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border-t-4 border-blue-500 p-6 flex flex-col h-full">
